value: Popular pieces : from the works of old French composers / selected, arranged for the pianoforte and revised by E. Pauer.

label: Old English composers for the virginals & harpsichord : a collection of preludes, galliards, pavanes, grounds, chaconnes, suites, overtures, sonatas, etc. selected from the works of / William Byrde, John Bull, Orlando Gibbons, John Blow, Henry Purcell and Thomas Augustine Arne ; revised & edited by E.
